22
00:02:39,067 --> 00:02:43,275
[KEPPI]
Kazuki, raging like a tsunami!

23
00:02:43,358 --> 00:02:47,358
Enta challenges him valiantly!

24
00:02:47,442 --> 00:02:49,067
[ENTA grunts]

25
00:02:49,150 --> 00:02:51,108
I don't have any
business doing sumo.

26
00:02:51,192 --> 00:02:54,150
My business is yours, too!

27
00:02:54,233 --> 00:02:56,317
[KEPPI] You're still in!
You're still in!

28
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:58,192
--You're still in, Kero!
--[ENTA yelling]

29
00:02:58,275 --> 00:03:00,608
[ENTA] My naked skin
pressed against his!

30
00:03:00,692 --> 00:03:03,317
Don't you hold back!
You know I want it all.

31
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:05,483
Kazuki, I...

32
00:03:05,567 --> 00:03:07,733
I'm about to lose it.

33
00:03:07,817 --> 00:03:11,358
[KAZUKI] Enta,
the Golden Duo never quits!

34
00:03:11,442 --> 00:03:14,067
[ENTA yells]

35
00:03:14,150 --> 00:03:17,150
--[ENTA] Another fantasy, huh?
--[KEPPI] A Kazuki victory!

36
00:03:17,233 --> 00:03:18,525
[KAZUKI]
Enta.

37
00:03:18,608 --> 00:03:22,067
Did you get hurt? Take my hand.

38
00:03:22,150 --> 00:03:24,025
There's no way this is real.

39
00:03:24,108 --> 00:03:25,442
--[snaps]
--[ENTA yells]

40
00:03:26,525 --> 00:03:29,108
--I'm not dreaming?
--[KEPPI] Uh-huh.

41
00:03:29,192 --> 00:03:32,317
[KAZUKI, ENTA]
<i>Kappas</i> for life!

42
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:33,858
[ALL laughing]

43
00:03:33,942 --> 00:03:35,400
[SARA]
Next on our plate,

44
00:03:35,483 --> 00:03:37,858
yesterday's flying
sachet incident continues,

45
00:03:37,942 --> 00:03:39,733
without any sign of stopping.

46
00:03:39,817 --> 00:03:42,233
Asakusa Police believe
a criminal organization

47
00:03:42,317 --> 00:03:44,983
is responsible,
but they don't have any leads.

48
00:03:45,067 --> 00:03:46,900
Sasheeeh!

49
00:03:46,983 --> 00:03:48,233
Funny.

50
00:03:48,317 --> 00:03:50,775
They're following up
on the story for once.

51
00:03:50,858 --> 00:03:52,525
Usually they just drop it.

52
00:03:52,608 --> 00:03:54,358
[ENTA]
I guess you're right, huh?

53
00:03:54,442 --> 00:03:57,192
Don't talk to me! Hmph!

54
00:03:59,733 --> 00:04:01,775
[ENTA] Hey, let's go
to the amusement park!

55
00:04:01,858 --> 00:04:04,317
People can't see us,
so we can get in for free!

56
00:04:05,567 --> 00:04:07,775
[gasps]
Hello, soccer ball!

57
00:04:07,858 --> 00:04:10,192
--And why are we here?
--Just for a laugh.

58
00:04:10,275 --> 00:04:13,025
It's where I used to change
into my Sara costume.

59
00:04:13,108 --> 00:04:14,942
Man, that was
pretty stupid, huh?

60
00:04:15,025 --> 00:04:16,400
Where'd I get that idea?

61
00:04:16,483 --> 00:04:18,567
--[KEPPI] <i>Kero</i> !
--[KAZUKI laughs]

62
00:04:18,650 --> 00:04:20,067
[TOI] You worked
pretty hard at it, though.

63
00:04:20,150 --> 00:04:21,192
[KEPPI]
Now me!

64
00:04:21,275 --> 00:04:22,692
[KAZUKI]
Well, it's all over now.

65
00:04:22,775 --> 00:04:25,192
Come on! Let's have some fun!

66
00:04:25,275 --> 00:04:29,150
-- <i>Kappas</i> for life!
--[KEPPI] <i>Kero</i> . Pole dance!

67
00:04:30,275 --> 00:04:33,317
Play it cool, and just give him
a pass, like old times.

68
00:04:33,400 --> 00:04:35,192
[KAZUKI]
Hey, Enta!

69
00:04:35,275 --> 00:04:37,067
Let's do this!

70
00:04:37,150 --> 00:04:38,567
